snippet.title: Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising – Nier Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome the sweet embrace of Death... Nier is the third new playable character joining the roster of Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising—coming out in 2023!
